08:09.122 --> 08:11.830
(Helicopter whirrs)

08:51.564 --> 08:53.703
(Both grunt)

09:20.060 --> 09:22.097
(Strains)

09:30.070 --> 09:31.606
(Neck cracks)

09:52.959 --> 09:57.271
Fuck it! Fuckin', fuckin' outrageous!

09:57.297 --> 09:59.903
I guess that means no needle.

10:01.434 --> 10:03.744
<i>If only, asshole.</i>

10:03.770 --> 10:07.616
We'd love to see you good and dead
like the innocents you slaughtered.

10:10.777 --> 10:13.280
But your friend has pulled some strings.

10:13.313 --> 10:15.657
I don't have any friends.

10:15.682 --> 10:17.855
Oh, no?

10:17.917 --> 10:21.421
It says here old Ironguts himself
has signed off on your release.

10:21.454 --> 10:23.365
I thought Thatcher was dead.

10:23.423 --> 10:25.027
Well, you thought wrong.

10:25.091 --> 10:28.265
It'll take more than a stroke
to kill that old warrior.

10:28.294 --> 10:29.967
Sign there.

10:34.701 --> 10:36.476
There and there.

10:43.476 --> 10:45.012
He's all yours.

11:10.970 --> 11:13.974
So, Mr Tyler -

11:14.007 --> 11:15.816
Rick -

11:15.842 --> 11:17.344
let's make a deal.

11:17.377 --> 11:20.415
I'm Meredith Baxter,
Senior VP with the network.

11:20.480 --> 11:24.360
Given the circumstances, I won't shake
your hand but consider us well-met.

11:24.384 --> 11:25.886
What is this?

11:25.919 --> 11:30.197
I'm the Executive Producer
of the most successful show on earth

11:30.223 --> 11:32.999
and... you're our new star.

11:34.994 --> 11:38.168
So now, just a quick briefing
and we're ready to play.

11:40.200 --> 11:41.941
Mr Tyler.

11:42.001 --> 11:43.674
Rick.

11:45.238 --> 11:46.876
I'm fucking this puppy -

11:46.906 --> 11:50.513
he's just lifting its tail,
so, stay with me, please.

11:52.245 --> 11:55.624
Turkey Shoot's the game,
and you're the Turkey.

11:55.682 --> 12:00.631
The game has three levels
and hidden in each level is this box.

12:00.687 --> 12:02.633
You have a GPS with its coordinates

12:02.689 --> 12:04.794
and the lock is activated
by your thumbprint.

12:04.857 --> 12:07.394
So, here's the deal.

12:07.427 --> 12:11.807
Locate and open the box within the time
limit, and proceed to the next level.

12:11.864 --> 12:14.470
Run out of time, and you're eliminated.

12:14.534 --> 12:18.641
Open all three boxes...
you win your freedom.

12:18.705 --> 12:20.707
Eliminated?

12:20.740 --> 12:24.813
It sounds a lot nicer than dead,
but that's what we're talking about.

12:24.877 --> 12:26.914
Life and death.

12:28.114 --> 12:29.991
- What the fuck is that?
(Device bleeps)

12:30.049 --> 12:32.962
Just a mild sedative
to introduce a tracking device

12:32.986 --> 12:35.626
so the cameras can always find you.

12:35.655 --> 12:39.159
Level 1 has four shooters,

12:39.225 --> 12:41.899
with double that amount
introduced each level.

12:41.928 --> 12:47.002
Their job is to hunt and kill you -
no prisoners, no mercy.

12:47.066 --> 12:50.479
Of course, you can return the favor.

12:51.738 --> 12:53.411
Any questions?

12:55.908 --> 12:58.149
What if I don't play'?

12:58.177 --> 13:01.317
Then you'll be a sitting duck.

13:03.449 --> 13:05.952
I studied your file, Rick.

13:07.287 --> 13:10.097
You survived combat, suicide missions,

13:10.123 --> 13:14.003
attempts on your life in prison,
even a bullet in the head.

13:15.128 --> 13:19.508
A guy like you...
just isn't wired to give up.

13:21.167 --> 13:24.205
You might even be our first winner.

13:24.270 --> 13:27.615
So... do we have a deal?

13:28.941 --> 13:30.614
What's in the box'?

13:35.014 --> 13:38.484
(Whispers) That's for me to know
and you to find out.

13:42.021 --> 13:43.659
Sleep now.

13:44.791 --> 13:49.240
When you wake... it's game on.

13:54.300 --> 14:00.683
ANNOUNCER:
Real criminals, real life, real time!

14:01.808 --> 14:05.153
You're watching smash hit event TV,

14:05.178 --> 14:09.388
coming at you right here, right now,

14:09.415 --> 14:11.361
wherever you are!

14:11.384 --> 14:15.264
(Cheering and applause)
- Turkey Shoot!

14:15.321 --> 14:17.927
It's live... with death.

14:17.990 --> 14:21.164
(Cheering and applause)

14:23.363 --> 14:30.872
Now let's give it up
for your hosts... Tom and Teena!

14:33.272 --> 14:34.842
I'm Teena Fine.

14:34.874 --> 14:36.376
And I'm Tom Faye.

14:36.409 --> 14:38.013
BOTH: Welcome to Turkey Shoot.

14:38.044 --> 14:41.082
Teena, last week's Turkey
just not up to the challenge.

14:41.114 --> 14:42.855
That's right, Tom.

14:42.882 --> 14:45.260
Convicted multiple murderess,
Olga Rashenko...

14:45.284 --> 14:47.924
- ..dubbed 'Satan's Babysitter'...
(Audience boos)

14:47.954 --> 14:51.561
ANNOUNCER: Straight from death row
in Russia's notorious Vladimir Prison,

14:51.591 --> 14:53.593
Teena, and playing for a pardon.

14:53.626 --> 14:58.041
Stumbled on the first level,
and didn't that make you happy?

14:58.064 --> 14:59.634
(Cheering and applause)

14:59.699 --> 15:01.372
(Gunshot)

15:05.238 --> 15:08.242
This time,
she met something a lot tougher

15:08.274 --> 15:10.777
than 14 defenceless children, Tom.

15:10.810 --> 15:14.656
That's right. She forgot one of
the golden rules of Turkey Shoot...

15:14.714 --> 15:17.820
(Gunshot)
(Cheering and whooping)

15:17.884 --> 15:20.228
And what is that rule'?

15:20.253 --> 15:22.392
AUDIENCE: Remember Ramrod!

15:22.422 --> 15:23.958
You got it.

15:23.990 --> 15:26.903
You should never forget
our most successful shooter ever.

15:26.926 --> 15:28.496
With 85 kills...

15:28.561 --> 15:30.063
ANNOUNCER: 86 now, Teena.

15:30.096 --> 15:33.270
Deadly from a mile, with a lethal smile.

15:33.299 --> 15:36.678
When he's in the game,
get ready for pain.

15:36.736 --> 15:38.943
ANNOUNCER:
The world's greatest marksman...

15:38.971 --> 15:40.507
BOTH: Ramrod!

15:40.573 --> 15:43.281
AUDIENCE: (Chants)
Ramrod! Ramrod! Ramrod! Ramrod!

15:43.309 --> 15:47.314
Afghanistan, Korea ll, World War Africa.

15:47.346 --> 15:49.690
The stats are unanimous, people.

15:49.749 --> 15:53.788
50,000 rounds expended
for every military kill.

15:53.820 --> 15:55.766
Now, the elite sniper...

15:57.857 --> 16:00.531
one round, one kill.

16:00.593 --> 16:04.006
The deadliest weapon in warfare...
(Chuckles)

16:04.030 --> 16:05.703
You're looking at him.

16:07.767 --> 16:11.874
Congratulations, Ramrod!
You just keep extending your record.

16:11.938 --> 16:13.781
Just doing my job, sir.

16:13.806 --> 16:15.308
86 in the trash.

16:15.341 --> 16:17.343
Don't be so modest, Ramrod.

16:17.376 --> 16:22.189
As the successful shooter, you're
now in Game 177, to do it all again.

16:22.215 --> 16:23.819
Looking forward, ma'am.

16:23.850 --> 16:26.330
Where you'll be joined
by three new shooters,

16:26.352 --> 16:29.196
as voted by our viewers worldwide.

16:29.222 --> 16:30.826
ANNOUNCER: That's right, Tom.

16:30.857 --> 16:34.498
The count is done and the results
are tallied, as smartphone voted by you!

16:34.527 --> 16:36.666
Individual territory charges applicable.

16:36.696 --> 16:40.303
Meet the shooters
for Turkey Shoot, Game 177.

16:40.333 --> 16:42.244
(Cheering and applause)

16:42.301 --> 16:45.544
The USA has voted Alpha!

16:45.571 --> 16:49.041
He's deadly with
primo weaponry.

16:49.075 --> 16:50.645
Alpha!

16:50.676 --> 16:53.520
Ooh... I love that guy.

16:55.548 --> 16:58.154
ANNOUNCER: Japan has elected Kintay -

16:58.184 --> 17:00.892
martial arts and ninja
smarts are her thing.

17:00.920 --> 17:02.422
Kintay!

17:02.488 --> 17:04.092
Awesome!

17:05.324 --> 17:09.670
ANNOUNCER: And the Middle East
is unanimous for Golgotha!

17:09.694 --> 17:13.268
He loves it up close and
personal with a blade.

17:13.332 --> 17:15.242
Golgotha!

17:15.268 --> 17:17.612
What a beast! Ramrod'?

17:17.670 --> 17:20.513
Good men all, sir - including her.

17:20.540 --> 17:22.041
(Laughter)

17:22.074 --> 17:24.577
OK, Tom, the suspense <i>is</i> killing me.

17:24.609 --> 17:26.589
Just who is our new Turkey?

17:26.612 --> 17:30.389
ANNOUNCER: Teena,
we've got someone very special for 177.

17:30.416 --> 17:32.293
He's a decorated soldier,

17:32.351 --> 17:37.232
court-martialled three years ago
for massacring women and children.

17:37.256 --> 17:38.894
He's Rick Tyler!

17:38.925 --> 17:41.371
- Disgraced former Navy SEAL...
(Audience boos)

17:41.394 --> 17:44.432
currently incarcerated
at Nee-Alcatraz Military Prison,

17:44.463 --> 17:47.933
where he's serving life,
plus a thousand years, for war crimes.

17:47.967 --> 17:50.379
My God! How can he live with himself?

17:50.403 --> 17:53.441
ANNOUNCER: He maintains
he has no memory of the killings, Teena,

17:53.472 --> 17:55.213
after being shot in the head.

17:55.241 --> 17:57.243
Uh-huh.

17:57.276 --> 18:01.952
So, Ramrod, a fellow soldier.
What do you say to that?

18:01.981 --> 18:04.325
Navy SEAL is Marine for 'pussy'.

18:04.383 --> 18:06.920
(Laughter) - Oh... Ramrod!

18:06.953 --> 18:08.660
I'm a jarhead, Torn.

18:08.721 --> 18:12.931
I say hoorah! Bring it.

18:12.959 --> 18:16.566
You heard it from the man.
It's game on!

18:16.596 --> 18:19.475
ANNOUNCER: With nothing but the clothes
on his back and a GPS,

18:19.498 --> 18:21.000
Turkey 177 will be dropped

18:21.067 --> 18:23.274
into the
Appalachian Mountains rainforest,

18:23.302 --> 18:25.339
approximately four miles
from the target.

18:27.473 --> 18:30.113
While avoiding four shooters
with a license to kill.

18:30.142 --> 18:32.418
Now...

18:32.445 --> 18:35.324
- Are you...
BOTH: Ready to play'?

18:35.348 --> 18:37.419
(Cheering and applause)

18:37.450 --> 18:40.294
ANNOUNCER:
It's time to go live on Level 1,

18:40.319 --> 18:44.961
for a rumble in the jungle,
where an ex-Navy SEAL takes on...

18:44.991 --> 18:46.993
Ramrod,

18:47.026 --> 18:48.767
Alpha.

18:48.794 --> 18:52.469
Golgotha and Kintay

18:52.498 --> 18:58.972
in Game 177 of Turkey Shoot!

18:59.005 --> 19:01.815
It's live... with death.

19:18.190 --> 19:21.034
(Rick pants heavily)

19:24.163 --> 19:27.235
(Panting continues)

19:39.378 --> 19:41.051
Agh!

19:41.080 --> 19:43.321
(Rick groans and splutters)

19:51.390 --> 19:53.336
(Birds squawk)

19:53.359 --> 19:55.862
(Insects buzz and chirp)

20:11.410 --> 20:13.856
(Water trickles)

20:18.350 --> 20:20.091
(Gasps)

20:21.387 --> 20:23.094
(Groans)

20:40.139 --> 20:43.245
(Bird screeches)

22:58.544 --> 23:01.184
Aghhh! (Grunts)

23:29.475 --> 23:31.079
(Both grunt)

23:31.110 --> 23:32.612
Fuck!

23:35.447 --> 23:37.484
(Gurgles)

23:46.926 --> 23:50.601
(Groans) Agh!

24:16.689 --> 24:18.691
(Chokes)

24:29.034 --> 24:30.604
(Gunshot)

24:32.371 --> 24:34.351
(Gunshots)

24:52.057 --> 24:53.798
Tricked that asshole.

25:21.353 --> 25:24.061
(Chuckles)
You ain't gonna make it, SEAL.

25:35.701 --> 25:37.374
Fuckin' numbnuts.

25:41.173 --> 25:42.914
I'd like some water, please.

25:51.784 --> 25:54.025
Got yourself a nice little hide-out.

25:58.123 --> 25:59.625
(Gunshot)

26:04.196 --> 26:07.439
You've gone soft, Llewyn. And stupid.

26:09.134 --> 26:10.636
It's 'Ramrod' now.

26:10.702 --> 26:13.740
What kind of fuckin' name is that'?

26:15.374 --> 26:16.978
That's cheating.

26:18.077 --> 26:20.250
That's the perks for being number one.

26:21.380 --> 26:23.621
Plus they really want you dead.

26:23.649 --> 26:25.322
They'?

26:25.384 --> 26:27.057
The powers that be.

26:27.086 --> 26:28.588
Thatcher?

26:28.620 --> 26:30.600
Even if I knew...

26:31.924 --> 26:33.961
Like shooting fish in a barrel.

26:35.060 --> 26:37.131
That's not very righteous.

26:38.597 --> 26:40.270
What happened to you'?

26:42.768 --> 26:45.840
Money, fame.

26:47.072 --> 26:49.018
See, I'm a celebrity now.

26:49.074 --> 26:50.985
(Chuckles)

26:51.009 --> 26:52.647
What are you'?

26:52.678 --> 26:54.783
The killer of women and children.

26:54.813 --> 26:56.622
Isn't that what you said at my trial?

26:56.648 --> 26:58.594
At least you remember that.

26:59.651 --> 27:01.653
They shoulda offed you in the brig.

27:01.687 --> 27:04.861
They tried - they died.

27:04.923 --> 27:06.925
Don't do it.

27:06.959 --> 27:09.872
I can tell you things
you don't remember.

27:09.928 --> 27:11.805
You didn't kill those kids.

27:13.165 --> 27:16.339
The massacre - you were framed.

27:17.970 --> 27:19.972
AUTOMATED VOICE: One minute remaining.

27:20.005 --> 27:22.281
59, 58...

27:22.307 --> 27:23.945
You're not going to make it, SEAL.

27:23.976 --> 27:25.478
57, 56...

27:25.511 --> 27:27.457
- I'll see you on the next level.
- ..55...

27:27.479 --> 27:29.049
Not if I see you first.

27:29.114 --> 27:30.650
53...

27:30.682 --> 27:35.688
34, 33, 32, 31...

27:35.721 --> 27:38.395
30 seconds remaining.

27:38.457 --> 27:42.200
18,17,16,

27:42.227 --> 27:47.836
15,14,13,12,11...

27:47.866 --> 27:50.312
10 seconds remaining.

27:50.335 --> 27:54.181
9, <i>8,</i> 7, 6...

28:35.380 --> 28:37.018
(Knocking at door)

28:40.118 --> 28:43.122
(Woman speaks indistinctly over PA)

28:47.359 --> 28:49.270
At ease, Commander.

28:52.231 --> 28:53.938
Did you bring it?

29:07.946 --> 29:09.983
Bunch of Nazis in this place.

29:10.048 --> 29:12.085
It is a hospital, sir.

29:12.117 --> 29:16.259
It's a filthy habit,
but when your days are numbered,

29:16.288 --> 29:19.895
you have to do what you want,
whatever the consequences.

29:23.228 --> 29:24.798
Did you watch it'?

29:24.830 --> 29:26.776
Yes, sir.

29:26.798 --> 29:29.404
I thought he looked good, considering.

29:31.136 --> 29:33.582
I didn't recognise Sergeant Llewyn.

29:33.605 --> 29:35.175
Ramrod?

29:37.643 --> 29:40.089
He's different since the trial.

29:40.112 --> 29:44.151
Profiting from death changes a person.

29:46.351 --> 29:49.457
So, you know we're sending in
a team to finish the job'?

29:49.488 --> 29:51.263
Yes, sir.

29:52.591 --> 29:54.798
I want you to pilot the chopper.

29:56.094 --> 29:59.473
Now, we both know that
Commander Tyler is a good soldier

29:59.498 --> 30:02.638
who would never divulge
classified intelligence,

30:02.668 --> 30:07.879
but my colleagues consider him a
loose end - and loose ends come undone.

30:09.174 --> 30:14.487
Commander... it is imperative
to the security of this nation

30:14.513 --> 30:16.515
that Rick Tyler be silenced.

30:16.548 --> 30:18.186
I can't tell you any more

30:18.216 --> 30:21.163
but know this position
is unanimous across command

30:21.186 --> 30:24.190
and goes right to the very top.

30:24.222 --> 30:25.724
Do you read me?

30:25.791 --> 30:27.464
In triplicate, sir.

30:30.629 --> 30:33.132
He should have died in that massacre.

30:34.499 --> 30:37.139
But if you want a clusterfuck,
send in the Marines.

30:38.370 --> 30:40.509
I don't understand, sir.

30:40.539 --> 30:42.985
What's not to understand, Commander?

30:45.010 --> 30:47.752
We framed Rick Tyler.

30:52.984 --> 30:56.727
