31:09.901 --> 31:12.347
They say only
the pure of heart sleep well.

31:13.905 --> 31:15.578
- Relax. (Device bleeps)

31:15.607 --> 31:18.383
It's a cocktail
of vitamins and antibiotics.

31:18.410 --> 31:23.519
It's cheating, I know, but I want you
to give Level <i>2</i> your best shot.

31:25.884 --> 31:27.420
How do you feel?

31:27.452 --> 31:29.295
Water.

31:35.861 --> 31:40.367
Decapitation, self-surgery,
that thing with the arrow -

31:40.399 --> 31:43.573
Game 177, so far, so amazing.

31:43.602 --> 31:45.047
The audience like you.

31:45.070 --> 31:48.244
No-one's retired
this many shooters before.

31:48.273 --> 31:51.811
You've even been voted a classic-kill
and you're not even halfway through.

31:51.877 --> 31:53.823
You haven't seen anything yet.

31:54.913 --> 31:56.620
Really?

31:56.648 --> 32:00.118
When I get Llewyn on the next level,
make sure all cameras are pointed at us.

32:00.152 --> 32:02.496
Ramrod.

32:02.554 --> 32:04.500
What is it with you two'?

32:06.324 --> 32:07.928
Wait and see.

32:12.564 --> 32:15.135
