32:17.335 --> 32:21.340
World War Africa -
a continent in meltdown...

32:22.674 --> 32:24.278
"with the President..."

32:24.309 --> 32:27.586
The Libyan dictator
must be removed.

32:27.612 --> 32:29.182
VOICE-OVER: ..her allies...

32:29.247 --> 32:34.162
I fully support my American counterpart
in our joint endeavors in Africa.

32:34.186 --> 32:36.427
