33:32.344 --> 33:34.551
- I'm Teena Fine.
- And I'm Tom Faye.

33:34.579 --> 33:36.183
BOTH: Welcome to Turkey Shoot.

33:36.214 --> 33:40.822
Teena, Turkey 177 - an army of one.

33:40.852 --> 33:42.525
You're not kidding, Tom.

33:42.554 --> 33:44.693
Ex-Navy SEAL Rick Tyler...

