<i>She puts the 'hun' into machinegun.</i>

34:51.056 --> 34:52.933
AUDIENCE: (Chants) Killshot! Killshot!

34:52.958 --> 34:54.938
- Killshot!
- What do you think, folks'?

34:57.094 --> 35:01.134
ANNOUNCER: Neo Korea
explodes for Armageddon!

35:01.166 --> 35:03.669
He's dyno-mite!

35:03.735 --> 35:05.772
Armageddon!

35:05.804 --> 35:07.806
Armageddon excited!

35:07.839 --> 35:09.341
(Laughter)

35:09.407 --> 35:12.183
ANNOUNCER: Well, get ready
for maximum excitement, Teena,

35:12.243 --> 35:15.781
because we've also got some
very extra special guest shooters

35:15.814 --> 35:17.418
for Level 2.

35:17.449 --> 35:22.262
Four crack Navy SEALs
from the disgraced Turkey's own platoon.

35:22.287 --> 35:23.857
- Wow! (Cheering and applause)

35:23.922 --> 35:25.765
They want some payback?

35:25.790 --> 35:27.326
ANNOUNCER: You got it, Tom.

35:27.359 --> 35:31.364
They've got an axe to grind...
in the Turkey's skull. Lieutenant?

35:31.429 --> 35:34.535
We've got a big chit to cash
with that mass-murdering son of a bitch.

35:34.599 --> 35:36.169
He brought disgrace on the SEALs.

35:36.201 --> 35:40.650
I can promise you now, we won't
stand down until honor's restored

35:40.672 --> 35:44.119
and the chit's paid... in blood.

35:44.142 --> 35:47.988
You heard it from the man.
These guys want vengeance!

35:48.013 --> 35:50.823
It's gonna be all-out war!

35:50.849 --> 35:53.455
ANNOUNCER: With the added advantage
of a pair of boots,

35:53.485 --> 35:56.022
Turkey 177 will wake
in the San Diego Docklands,

35:56.054 --> 35:58.159
approximately one mile from the target.

35:58.189 --> 36:00.465
He has exactly 90 minutes
to reach his goal,

36:00.492 --> 36:04.634
while avoiding eight killers, armed to
the teeth and out for his blood.

36:04.663 --> 36:06.233
Now...

36:06.297 --> 36:09.835
- Are you...
BOTH: Ready to play'?

36:09.868 --> 36:13.680
ANNOUNCER: It's time to go live
in an eight-to-one showdown

36:13.705 --> 36:15.582
when Rick Tyler takes on...

36:15.640 --> 36:18.917
Ramrod, Haakon,

36:18.977 --> 36:22.481
Killshot, Armageddon

36:22.514 --> 36:25.825
and four SEALs on Level 2 of...

36:25.850 --> 36:28.729
Turkey Shoot!

36:28.753 --> 36:31.859
It's live... with death.

36:40.565 --> 36:43.876
(Motorcycle revs)

38:08.253 --> 38:10.290
Say hello to my little friends.

38:26.938 --> 38:31.216
(High-pitched ringing)

38:47.725 --> 38:49.363
(Rick groans)

38:55.233 --> 38:56.837
(Rick grunts)

39:02.740 --> 39:04.185
Ha!

39:04.209 --> 39:05.882
(Armageddon groans)

39:13.051 --> 39:15.759
(Thunder crashes)

39:17.989 --> 39:19.866
(Both grunt)

39:43.214 --> 39:45.854
(Neck cracks)

39:51.456 --> 39:54.403
(Thunder crashes)

40:05.637 --> 40:10.484
(Helicopter whirrs overhead)

40:29.827 --> 40:31.431
SOLDIER: Keep tight, keep tight.

40:32.730 --> 40:34.573
OK, keep... keep tight, come on.

40:34.599 --> 40:36.943
SOLDIER 2: Two exits here.
Two exits, I got two.

40:38.603 --> 40:40.105
Clear!

40:42.941 --> 40:45.080
Open season!

40:48.646 --> 40:50.489
Yahh!

40:50.515 --> 40:53.086
(Distant gunfire)

41:23.214 --> 41:24.989
Aghh.

41:26.451 --> 41:28.453
(Both grunt)

41:32.156 --> 41:34.067
SOLDIER: Go, go, go, go, go, go!

41:35.293 --> 41:36.863
Clear!

41:36.894 --> 41:38.896
(Grunts and groans)

41:38.963 --> 41:40.670
SOLDIER: Keep tight.

41:53.745 --> 41:55.383
- Clear.
- Clear.

42:09.427 --> 42:11.100
- Agh! (Gunshot)

42:14.399 --> 42:18.279
(Rick grunts)

42:47.965 --> 42:50.206
- Clear.
- Clear.

42:56.274 --> 42:57.878
SOLDIER: Contact!

42:59.277 --> 43:01.154
Pursue! Pursue!

43:01.212 --> 43:03.385
- Go, go, go, go, go, go!
- Forward! Forward!

43:06.651 --> 43:08.255
Target! Target!

43:08.286 --> 43:09.890
(Gunfire)

43:17.161 --> 43:18.936
Left and right, left and right.

43:26.571 --> 43:28.141
SOLDIER: Fall back! Fall back!

43:28.172 --> 43:30.516
Get down!

43:32.410 --> 43:34.253
(Soldier shouts indistinctly)

43:41.519 --> 43:43.089
Target!

43:44.922 --> 43:48.301
(Distant gunfire)

43:53.197 --> 43:54.767
Keep tight, keep tight.

43:54.799 --> 43:57.780
- Keep tight, keep tight, come on.
- Go through. Go through.

43:59.937 --> 44:01.939
- Keep moving, just keep moving.
- Clear.

44:07.812 --> 44:09.485
- Agh!
- Are you alright?

44:11.649 --> 44:13.458
Get back, get back. Get outta there.

44:14.552 --> 44:16.361
Keep tight, keep tight, come on.

44:16.387 --> 44:19.664
Guys, keep together. Keep working
the sides, keep working the sides.

44:22.627 --> 44:24.129
Keep moving, keep moving.

44:24.162 --> 44:25.664
Clear.

44:26.731 --> 44:29.507
SOLDIER: Come on, keep together.
We're splitting up here.

44:31.669 --> 44:33.239
Man down!

44:34.872 --> 44:36.647
<i>Go, go, 90, 90, go!</i>

44:36.674 --> 44:38.483
Go, go, go!

44:38.509 --> 44:40.318
Man down! Man down!

44:44.315 --> 44:46.317
SOLDIER: Get him out of here,
get him out.

44:47.552 --> 44:49.225
(Distant gunfire)

44:49.253 --> 44:51.392
You fuckin' piece of shit.

45:00.698 --> 45:02.371
<i>Go, go, 90, 90, go!</i>

45:54.285 --> 45:55.787
Fucker.

46:12.603 --> 46:14.173
Fucker.

46:21.345 --> 46:23.018
(Gunshot)

46:24.181 --> 46:25.854
(Gunshot)

46:32.290 --> 46:33.860
Now, you fucker...

46:46.971 --> 46:48.473
Fuck it!

47:12.997 --> 47:14.840
Commander Wilson?

47:15.966 --> 47:17.707
What the fuck is going on here?

47:17.735 --> 47:20.011
What's it look like?
I just saved your ass.

47:21.172 --> 47:23.015
(Rapid bleeping)

47:23.040 --> 47:24.542
Shit!

47:25.910 --> 47:27.651
Putting her down.

47:59.377 --> 48:01.755
Excuse me, sir,
we have a military emergency.

48:01.779 --> 48:03.383
I need to commandeer your vehicle.

48:03.414 --> 48:05.416
Yes, ma'am. Is that a Black Hawk?

48:05.449 --> 48:07.690
I need you to stay here
with the Black Hawk, sir,

48:07.718 --> 48:09.220
while we take your vehicle.

48:09.253 --> 48:11.392
- Terrorists?
- I'm not at liberty to say, sir.

48:12.590 --> 48:15.628
- I just filled her up.
- Your country thanks you, sir.

48:15.693 --> 48:17.297
(fires screech)

48:19.964 --> 48:21.466
That was easy.

48:21.532 --> 48:24.103
Hard word gets them every time.

48:24.135 --> 48:26.206
AUTOMATED VOICE: One minute remaining.

48:26.237 --> 48:28.046
- Piece of fuckin' shit!
- ..59...

48:29.140 --> 48:30.915
Christ, you stink.

48:32.576 --> 48:34.214
And you look like shit.

48:34.245 --> 48:36.282
So is this part of the Turkey Shoot
as well?

48:36.313 --> 48:40.784
Fuck Turkey Shoot. 24 hours ago, I was
happy for you to rot in jail forever.

48:40.818 --> 48:43.321
Then I found out
you didn't kill those children.

48:44.655 --> 48:46.259
Found out?

48:46.290 --> 48:48.668
Thatcher told me
you were framed for the massacre.

48:50.728 --> 48:52.264
He told you'?

48:52.296 --> 48:54.276
The question is, why'?

48:54.298 --> 48:56.073
Why were you framed'?

48:58.335 --> 49:01.179
Hey, I just ruined
a brilliant career for you, asshole.

49:01.238 --> 49:02.945
You owe me an answer.

49:05.242 --> 49:06.812
Tell me.

49:09.980 --> 49:11.516
Hick?

49:13.651 --> 49:16.962
I assassinated the Libyan dictator
two weeks before the invasion.

49:18.789 --> 49:21.133
A black op, on the President's orders.

49:21.158 --> 49:23.263
Her last-ditch effort to avoid war.

49:27.031 --> 49:28.669
(Tyres screech)

49:30.167 --> 49:31.669
He's dead'?

49:31.702 --> 49:33.704
I watched his head explode.

49:34.805 --> 49:38.275
But the Libyans put in a double,
like we knew they would.

49:38.309 --> 49:41.779
But the Generals told the President
that my mission was a failure.

49:41.812 --> 49:43.655
Thatcher wanted war.

49:43.681 --> 49:45.524
And you're the loose end.

49:47.551 --> 49:50.122
The only one besides them
who knows the truth.

49:50.154 --> 49:51.792
I can't believe it.

49:51.822 --> 49:56.202
This whole shitty war is about
killing someone who's already dead.

49:57.828 --> 50:00.809
- Why didn't you try and say something?
- I didn't have any proof.

50:00.831 --> 50:03.573
- But at your trial you could've...
- Who would you believe?

50:03.634 --> 50:05.739
A psychopathic killer
of women and children,

50:05.803 --> 50:07.840
or four-star generals?

50:14.478 --> 50:16.549
We've got to deal with
that tracking device

50:16.580 --> 50:18.685
or we'll never even
make it out of the county.

50:20.050 --> 50:23.827
â™ª [EERIE MUSIC]

50:23.854 --> 50:27.700
(Echoing shouts and screams)

50:40.104 --> 50:41.708
Wrap this around you.

50:52.082 --> 50:53.720
Will this work'?

50:53.751 --> 50:58.461
If it doesn't, it's been nice
seeing you again, Commander.

50:58.522 --> 51:00.297
Likewise, Commander.

51:03.127 --> 51:04.970
Sorry I got angry before.

51:05.029 --> 51:06.872
It's a lot to take in.

51:08.132 --> 51:09.702
Somethings still bothering me.

51:10.768 --> 51:13.044
Why did Thatcher tell you
I was innocent?

51:14.104 --> 51:16.448
He never does anything without a reason.

51:17.942 --> 51:20.548
I'll be sure to ask him,
right before I kill him.

51:22.079 --> 51:24.650
Go back to sleep
while I find us a motel.

51:26.617 --> 51:29.097
Whatever happens, thank you.

51:33.924 --> 51:35.494
You're welcome, Rick.

51:58.248 --> 52:02.287
I don't care if his tumor
is having a triple fucking bypass,

52:02.319 --> 52:05.095
you tell his people
if I don't speak with General Thatcher

52:05.122 --> 52:09.093
in the next 15 minutes,
he's gonna wish he was dead.

52:14.865 --> 52:16.367
(Speaks in foreign language)

52:22.506 --> 52:25.112
GENERAL THATCHER, ON PHONE:
Good morning, Meredith.

52:25.142 --> 52:26.678
Where is he, General?

52:26.710 --> 52:28.519
I'm not too bad, thank you for asking.

52:28.545 --> 52:31.719
Don't fuck with me, Thatcher.
Where's my Turkey?

52:31.782 --> 52:34.558
Calm down, Meredith,
I've got my best people on it.

52:34.618 --> 52:38.191
Don't patronise me, you asshole.
I know you're behind this.

52:38.222 --> 52:39.826
I thought we had a deal.

52:39.857 --> 52:42.736
I had nothing to do with it.
One of my people went rogue.

52:42.793 --> 52:44.363
These things happen.

52:44.395 --> 52:47.706
This is television, Chuck,
nothing happens on television -

52:47.731 --> 52:49.369
not on my network.

52:49.400 --> 52:52.074
We'll find him, Meredith.
You have my word on that.

52:52.136 --> 52:54.844
If I don't get him back
within the next 12 hours, General,

52:54.872 --> 52:57.375
that cancer of yours
is going to have to get in line,

52:57.408 --> 52:59.410
because I will fucking bury you.

54:09.713 --> 54:12.592
(Device clicks)

54:14.418 --> 54:17.092
Knee reconstruction - metal pins.

54:22.092 --> 54:23.594
Nothing there?

54:23.627 --> 54:25.300
Keep moving, soldier.

54:35.139 --> 54:36.982
(Device clicks)

54:37.007 --> 54:38.611
Bullet.

54:46.750 --> 54:48.593
(Device clicks) - Metal plate.

54:50.187 --> 54:51.689
Roll over.

55:04.434 --> 55:06.004
(Device clicks)

55:06.036 --> 55:07.538
Anything there?

55:08.705 --> 55:10.343
Not that I know of.

55:12.976 --> 55:14.546
Found it.

55:28.992 --> 55:31.404
- You ready?
- Uh-huh.

55:31.461 --> 55:34.067
This is gonna hurt you
a lot more than me.

55:37.000 --> 55:38.638
Oh, fuck!

55:46.310 --> 55:47.812
Gotcha.

55:54.351 --> 55:56.661
(Device crunches)

55:59.489 --> 56:01.059
Now...

56:05.062 --> 56:06.564
hold still.

56:14.538 --> 56:18.953
(Echoing shouts and screams)

56:30.888 --> 56:36.304
32 seconds - you manipulate it
well, my dear, like part of your body.

56:36.360 --> 56:38.237
It is my own design.

56:38.262 --> 56:40.640
Yes, a very nice piece. Mm.

56:40.697 --> 56:42.699
And what did you bring
for the hunt, Tito?

56:42.733 --> 56:44.371
Something excessive, I imagine.

56:44.401 --> 56:45.971
Of course, my dear.

56:46.036 --> 56:51.952
After all, excess is what makes
life worth living for people like us.

56:51.975 --> 56:54.046
If I had more men like you
in the department,

56:54.077 --> 56:57.149
I wouldn't have all these problems
with these blasted deviants.

56:57.214 --> 57:01.162
MAN, ON TV': Yes, sir. Kill 'em.
No fancy stuff - just kill 'em all.

57:01.218 --> 57:03.664
- What took you so long?
TITO: The ultimate solution.

57:03.720 --> 57:05.791
Food, clothes.
- You're a sharp man.

57:07.057 --> 57:08.627
And I got us a car.

57:08.659 --> 57:11.799
MAN, ON TV: Anything you want, sir,
just let me know.

57:11.828 --> 57:13.330
TITO: Hitler...

57:13.397 --> 57:14.899
Are you having any?

57:14.932 --> 57:16.468
I'm gonna take a shower.

57:16.500 --> 57:20.141
It's an amazing twist
in an amazing game, Tom.

57:20.170 --> 57:24.414
You said it, Teena.
The Turkey's gone and the hunt is on!

57:24.441 --> 57:28.617
And just who is this mysterious
blonde bombshell helping him?

57:28.645 --> 57:32.149
ANNOUNCER: She's been identified
as Commander Jillian Wilson,

57:32.182 --> 57:37.188
a fellow Navy SEAL and an ace
chopper pilot - as if we didn't know!

57:37.254 --> 57:39.461
And check the live stats, people.

57:39.489 --> 57:41.469
(Cheering and applause)

57:41.491 --> 57:44.631
Rick Tyler's approval rating
is off the charts.

57:44.661 --> 57:46.163
Wow!

57:46.196 --> 57:49.143
You guys are really liking this Turkey.

57:49.166 --> 57:52.841
We all love a man
who can take charge, Tom.

57:52.869 --> 57:55.713
ANNOUNCER: But let's not forget
what Rick Tyler is, Teena -

57:55.772 --> 57:58.810
a cold-blooded killer
of innocent women and children.

57:58.842 --> 58:02.813
Even battle-hardened veterans
were shocked by the insane bloodlust

58:02.846 --> 58:07.317
exhibited in one of the worst rogue
killing sprees ever seen in combat.

58:07.351 --> 58:11.390
That single act of merciless carnage,
perpetrated against unarmed...

58:17.394 --> 58:20.204
For three years,
I thought that fuck was me.

58:22.666 --> 58:26.546
I remember the kids, the village
and waking up in a hospital in Germany.

58:29.840 --> 58:34.585
I can't remember the massacre.
But I knew I was guilty.

58:37.848 --> 58:39.555
Now you know the truth.

58:41.051 --> 58:42.758
Being innocent doesn't matter.

58:43.854 --> 58:45.527
Knowing you can do it...

58:47.190 --> 58:50.171
I've killed a lot of people, Jill,
and felt nothing.

59:06.910 --> 59:08.514
Maybe I don't have a heart.

01:00:12.976 --> 01:00:14.512
RICK: Which hospital is he in'?

01:00:14.578 --> 01:00:16.580
JILL: There is no way
I'm taking you there.

01:00:16.613 --> 01:00:18.593
The place will be crawling
with security.

01:00:18.615 --> 01:00:20.754
RICK: That's never stopped me before.

01:00:20.784 --> 01:00:23.162
JILL: Don't be crazy.
Thatcher's not worth it.

01:00:23.186 --> 01:00:25.188
RICK: I wanna see him.

01:00:25.255 --> 01:00:28.429
I mean it, Rick, it's too dangerous.
Just forget the General.

01:00:28.458 --> 01:00:29.994
Let's disappear.

01:00:30.026 --> 01:00:32.267
You realise he's planned
this whole thing.

01:00:32.295 --> 01:00:35.037
- He wants me to get to him.
- Bullshit.

01:00:35.098 --> 01:00:37.305
He knows you, Jill, and he knows me.

01:00:37.334 --> 01:00:39.007
He knew you'd do something.

01:00:39.035 --> 01:00:40.639
He's crippled and helpless.

01:00:40.670 --> 01:00:43.651
You know what that means for
a guy like him? He's already in hell.

01:00:43.673 --> 01:00:45.846
Killing him is just doing him a favor.

01:00:45.876 --> 01:00:48.550
I'm not gonna kill him -
it's not about revenge anymore.

01:00:48.612 --> 01:00:50.285
Then what's it about?

01:00:50.313 --> 01:00:52.020
I don't know.

01:00:56.219 --> 01:00:57.823
(Siren wails)

01:00:57.854 --> 01:00:59.390
Shit!

01:01:04.127 --> 01:01:05.629
Fuck!

01:01:05.662 --> 01:01:08.575
(Siren blares)

01:01:08.632 --> 01:01:09.702
Hold On!

01:01:09.900 --> 01:01:12.380
(fires screech)

01:01:19.075 --> 01:01:20.577
(indistinct radio chatter)

01:01:20.644 --> 01:01:22.180
(Crash!)

01:01:27.317 --> 01:01:30.059
(Siren continues wailing)

01:01:41.765 --> 01:01:45.269
NEWSREADER: Breaking news this hour.
I'm Pete Sanchez.

01:01:45.335 --> 01:01:48.714
Chaos in the downtown tunnels
as authorities pursue a high-speed chase

01:01:48.738 --> 01:01:52.015
causing a score of pile-ups
and creating gridlock across the city.

01:01:52.042 --> 01:01:53.544
Police say the vehicle,

01:01:53.577 --> 01:01:57.354
believed to contain the mass murderer
whose dramatic escape from Turkey Shoot

01:01:57.380 --> 01:01:58.882
has amazed the world,

01:01:58.915 --> 01:02:01.225
has been lost
in the serpentine transit system.

01:02:01.251 --> 01:02:04.596
Crossing now to the network's
eye in the sky for live developments.

01:02:04.621 --> 01:02:06.123
Here's Gina Jones.

01:02:06.189 --> 01:02:07.691
GINA JONES: Thanks, Pete.

01:02:07.724 --> 01:02:10.933
The network can report
that the chase is back on,

01:02:10.961 --> 01:02:13.635
after the
pale-or white-colored vehicle,

01:02:13.697 --> 01:02:18.908
believed to contain escaped Turkey
Rick Tyler and his beautiful accomplice,

01:02:18.935 --> 01:02:22.747
dramatically reappeared at the L21 exit.

01:02:25.775 --> 01:02:28.255
(Sirens blare, tires screech)

01:02:34.918 --> 01:02:38.092
WOMAN, OVER PA: Dr Schwartz,
please report to Oncology.

01:02:40.123 --> 01:02:43.161
REPORTER: SEAL Commander
Jillian Wilson surrendered to police

01:02:43.226 --> 01:02:44.933
after a crash ended the chase.

01:02:44.961 --> 01:02:48.340
But the convicted mass murderer
remains at large this hour,

01:02:48.398 --> 01:02:50.844
as a manhunt continues downtown.

01:02:50.900 --> 01:02:53.437
It is believed
Turkey Shoot escapee Rick Tyler

